Requirements: Apple Quicktime (install before Juicer3)

1) Install the "Juicer3.88_Build100.exe" from the setup folder
2) Copy the "main.exe" from the crack folder to the Juicer installation directory and overwrite
3) Insert the DJ index disk into your DVD drive, or mount the ISO image
4) Run the Juicer3 app. From the "File" menu select the "Install Products...", select the index disk item and install
5) When asked, enter an email address and a serial number of your choise and complete the installation.
